@startuml Garment
title Sequence Diagram: Garment Upload and Management

actor Retailer

boundary "Frontend\n(React)" as Frontend
control "Backend\n(FastAPI)" as Backend
control "Garment Processing\nModule" as GPM
database "PostgreSQL" as DB

Retailer -> Frontend : Enter garment details\n(images, sizes, measurements)
activate Frontend

Frontend -> Backend : Submit garment information
activate Backend

Backend -> GPM : Validate garment data
activate GPM

GPM -> GPM : Validate required fields
GPM -> GPM : Verify measurements
GPM -> GPM : Process garment images

GPM --> Backend : Validated garment information
deactivate GPM

Backend -> DB : Save garment information
activate DB

DB --> Backend : Garment stored successfully
deactivate DB

Backend --> Frontend : Upload successful
deactivate Backend

Frontend --> Retailer : Display confirmation
deactivate Frontend

@enduml